he History of the Black Experience Through Documents'' (2001)\n\n==External links==\n{{NIE Poster|Negro in America|African-American history}}\n{{wikiquote}}\n{{div col}}\n* {{cite web|url=https://familysearch.org/learn/wiki/en/African_American_Place_of_Origin|title=African American Place of Origin Genealogy - FamilySearch Wiki|website=Familysearch.org|accessdate= October 25, 2017}}\n* [http://www.todayinafricanamericanhistory.com A daily look into the great events and people in African American history]\n* [http://www.visionaryproject.org/videos Pioneering African American oral history video excerpts] at The National Visionary Leadership Project\n* [http://blackhistorydaily.com Black History Daily - 365 days of Black History]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20120107214249/http://www.aawc.com/aah.html African-American history connection]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20071017063102/http://www.africanamericanhistory.tv/ \"African American History Channel\"] - African-American History Channel\n* [https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/aia \"Africans in America\"] - PBS 4-Part Series (2007)\n*[https://www.pbs.org/opb/historydetectives/investigations/602_redhandflag.html] PBS Red Hand flag Episode 2008\n* [https://www.amazon.com/dp/0465043895 Living Black History:] How Reimagining the African-American Past Can Remake America's Racial Future by [http://www.manningmarable.net/ Dr. Manning Marable] (2006)\n* [https://www.loc.gov/rr/mss/guide/african.html Library of Congress] - African American History and Culture\n* [http://memory.loc.gov/ammem/aaohtml/exhibit/aointro.html Library of Congress] - African American Odyssey \n* [http://www.columbia.edu/cu/ccbh/ Center for Contemporary Black History] at Columbia University\n* [http://search.eb.com/Blackhistory/home.do ''Encyclop\u00e6dia Britannica'' - Guide to Black History]\n* [http://www.sos.mo.gov/archives/resources/africanamerican/intro.asp Missouri State Archives - African-American History Initiative]\n* [http://www.blackhistory.com B