e=radiodate.it|language=Italian}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{MetroLyrics song|keala-settle-the-greatest-showman-ensemble|this-is-me}}\n\n{{Golden Globe Award for Best Original Song 2010s}}\n{{Kesha}}\n\n[[Category:2017 singles]]\n[[Category:2017 songs]]\n[[Category:Kesha songs]]\n[[Category:Missy Elliott songs]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Justin Paul (songwriter)]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Benj Pasek]]\n[[Category:Best Original Song Golden Globe winning songs]]\n[[Category:Atlantic Records singles]]\n[[Category:Songs written for films]]\n[[Category:Song recordings produced by Greg Wells]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2017 single by Keala Settle}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:This Is Me (''The Greatest Showman'' song)}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = This Is Me\n| cover      =\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Keala Settle]] and ''[[The Greatest Showman]]'' Ensemble\n| album      = [[The Greatest Showman: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack]]\n| released   = December 8, 2017\n| format     = [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| recorded   = 2017\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = [[Pop music|Pop]]\n| length     = {{Duration|m=3|s=54}}\n| label      = [[Atlantic Records|Atlantic]]\n| writer     = [[Benj Pasek and Justin Paul]]\n| producer   = [[Greg Wells]], [[Justin Paul]], [[Adam Gubman]], [[Alex Lacamoire]]\n| chronology = [[Keala Settle]]\n| prev_title =\n| prev_year  =\n| next_title = [[Bird Set Free#Keala Settle version|Bird Set Free]]\n| next_year  = 2018\n| misc       = {{Extra chronology\n | artist     = [[The Greatest Showman: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack|The Greatest Showman]] soundtrack\n | type       = singles\n | prev_title =\n | prev_year  =\n | title      = This Is Me\n | year       = 2017\n | next_title = [[Rewrite the Stars]]\n | next_year  = 2018\n}}\n}}\n\"'''This Is Me'''\" is a song performed by [[Keala Settle]] for the film ''[[The Greatest Showman]]''. It was released on October 26, 2017, by [[Atlantic Records]] as a promotional single from ''[[The Greatest Showman: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack]]''<ref>{{cite web |title=The Greatest Showman |url=https://www.amazon.com/Greatest-Showman-Original-Picture-Soundtrack/dp/B076Q58K3T |website=[[Amazon.com]] |accessdate=January 9, 2018}}</ref> and the official lead single on December 8, 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Keala+Settle+%26+The+Greatest+Showman+Ensemble&titel=This+Is+Me&cat=s|title= KEALA SETTLE & THE GREATEST SHOWMAN ENSEMBLE - THIS IS ME (SONG)|publisher=Australian Charts|accessdate=July 25, 2018}}</ref> It won the [[Golden Globe Award for Best Original Song]] at the [[75th Golden Globe Awards]] and was nominated for an [[Academy Award for Best Original Song]] at the [[90th Academy Awards]] but lost to \"[[Remember Me (Coco song)|Remember Me]]\" from the film ''[[Coco (2017 film)|Coco]]''.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/the-greatest-showman-benj-pasek-justin-paul-oscars-interview-1202195785/ |title=The Greatest Showman Songwriters Benj Pasek & Justin Paul On The Revitalization Of The Original Hollywood Musical |last=Grobar |first=Matt |date=November 17, 2017 |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]}}</ref> It was later nominated for the [[Grammy Award for Best Song Written for Visual Media]] at the [[61st Annual Grammy Awards]].\n\nFollowing the film's global release, the song charted within the top five in the United Kingdom, the top ten in Australia, Ireland, Malaysia, and South Korea and the top twenty in Belgium (Flanders) and New Zealand.\n\n== Live performances ==\nThe song was first previewed by [[Hugh Jackman]] in Australia during his 2015 [[Broadway to Oz]] tour.<ref>[https://dailyreview.com.au/hugh-jackman-broadway-to-oz-review-rod-laver-arena-melbourne/33673/ Hugh Jackman: Broadway to Oz review (Rod Laver Arena, Melbourne) | Daily Review: Film, stage and music reviews, interviewa and more.]</ref> Keala Settle performed \"This Is Me\" live at [[Vision Australia]]'s Carols by Candlelight at the [[Sidney Myer Music Bowl]] in Melbourne, Australia on December 24, 2017.<ref>{{cite web |title=This Is Me - Keala Settle (The Greatest Showman) (Feat. Melbourne Gospel Choir) #carolsbycandlelight |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D0MTBJ2xIc8 |website=Youtube |publisher=Melbourne Gospel Choir |accessdate=November 14, 2018}}</ref> She also performed at the Carols by Candlelight Rehearsal on December 23, 2017 and followed up with an encore performance. Settle performed the song live on ''[[The Graham Norton Show]]'' on February 9, 2018.<ref>{{Cite news |title=Who is on The Graham Norton Show tonight \u2013 guests include Saoirse Ronan, Will & Grace stars and Rob Beckett |url=http://metro.co.uk/2018/02/09/graham-norton-show-tonight-guests-include-saoirse-ronan-will-grace-stars-rob-beckett-7298323/ |work=[[Metro (website)|Metro]] |last=Duncan |first=Amy |date=February 9, 2018 |accessdate=February 24, 2018}}</ref> Later she performed on ''[[The Ellen DeGeneres Show]]'' on February 21, 2018.<ref>{{Cite news |title=Greatest Showman' Star Keala Settle Sings 'This Is Me' on 'Ellen' |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8213442/the-greatest-showman-keala-settle-this-is-me-on-ellen |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |last=Braca |first=Nina |date=February 21, 2018 |accessdate=February 24, 2018}}</ref> She also performed the song at the [[90th Academy Awards]] ceremony on March 4, 2018.\n\n==Track listings==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Instrumental<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/this-is-me-from-the-greatest-showman-instrumental-single/1353161929|title=This Is Me (Instrumental) \u2013 Single|work=iTunes Store (AU)|accessdate=July 25, 2018}}</ref>\n| extra_column = Artist\n| title1  = This Is Me\n| note1 = instrumental\n| extra1 = ''The Greatest Showman'' Ensemble\n| length1 = 3:54\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| headline = [[Dave Aud\u00e9]] remix<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/this-is-me-dave-aud\u00e9-remix-from-the-greatest-showman-single/1344025370|title=This Is Me (Dave Aud\u00e9 Remix) \u2013 Single|work=iTunes Store (AU)|accessdate=July 25, 2018}}</ref>\n| extra_column = Artist\n| title1  = This Is Me\n| note1 = Dave Aud\u00e9 remix\n| extra1 = [[Keala Settle]] and ''The Greatest Showman'' Ensemble\n| length1 = 3:36\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| headline = [[Alan Walker (producer)|Alan Walker]] relift<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/this-is-me-alan-walker-relift-from-greatest-showman/1360236761|title=This Is Me (Alan Walker Relift) \u2013 Single|work=iTunes Store (AU)|accessdate=July 25, 2018}}</ref>\n| extra_column = Artist\n| title1  = This Is Me\n| note1 = Alan Walker relift\n| extra1 = Keala Settle and ''The Greatest Showman'' Ensemble\n| length1 = 3:35\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Spanish version<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/as%C3%AD-soy-from-the-greatest-showman-single/1326361815|title=As\u00ed Soy (From \"The Greatest Showman\") - Single by Maite Perroni & The Greatest Showman Ensemble on Apple Music|publisher=[[iTunes Store]]|accessdate=November 22, 2018}}</ref>\n| extra_column = Artist\n| title1  = As\u00ed Soy\n| extra1 = [[Maite Perroni]] and ''The Greatest Showman'' Ensemble\n| length1 = 3:55\n}}\n\n== Charts ==\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-2}}\n=== Weekly charts ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2017\u201319)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|10|artist=Keala Settle & The Greatest Showman Ensemble|song=This Is Me|rowheader=true|accessdate=January 20, 2018}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|31|artist=Keala Settle & The Greatest Showman Ensemble|song=This Is Me|rowheader=true|accessdate=February 1, 2018}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders|41|artist=Keala Settle & The Greatest Showman Ensemble|song=This