ei province in China following coronavirus outbreak |date=5 February 2020 |work=[[The Tufts Daily]] |publisher=Tufts University |location=Medford, Massachusetts |access-date=17 February 2020}} * {{cite web |url=https://news.psu.edu/story/607202/2020/02/06/campus-life/student-organizations-penn-state-rally-help-wuhan |title=Student organizations at Penn State rally to help Wuhan |work=Penn State: News |publisher=[[Pennsylvania State University]] |access-date=17 February 2020}} * {{cite web |url=https://www.stanforddaily.com/2020/02/06/stanford-for-wuhan-sends-medical-supplies-to-coronavirus-victims/ |title=Stanford for Wuhan sends medical supplies to coronavirus victims |date=7 February 2020 |work=[[The Stanford Daily]] |publisher=Stanford University |access-date=17 February 2020}} * {{cite web |url=https://ndsmcobserver.com/2020/01/chinese-students-respond-to-supply-shortages-throughout-hospitals-in-wuhei-providence-in-the-midst-of-coronavirus-outbreak/ |title=Chinese students respond to supply shortages throughout hospitals in Wuhan City in the midst of coronavirus outbreak |date=31 January 2020 |work=The Observer<!--not [[The Observer]]--> |publisher=[[University of Notre Dame]] / [[Holy Cross College (Indiana)|Holy Cross College]] / [[Saint Mary's College (Indiana)|Saint Mary's College]] |location=Notre Dame, Indiana |url-status=live |access-date=17 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"20200128directrelief\">{{cite web |url=https://www.directrelief.org/2020/01/direct-relief-rushes-facial-masks-to-china-to-fight-coronavirus-spread/ |title=Direct Relief Rushes Facial Masks to China to Fight Coronavirus Spread |last= |date=28 January 2020 |work=DirectRelief.org |publisher=[[Direct Relief]] |access-date=29 January 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-180\">{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/lisettevoytko/2020/02/05/bill-and-melinda-gates-donate-100-million-to-coronavirus-vaccine-research/ |title=Bill And Melinda Gates Donate $100 Million to Coronavirus Vaccine Re